Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.63,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}注视着你 Red eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:24.30,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}一直在寻找真理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:28.64,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}却在彷徨中迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:35.23,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1300)\blur3\be3}万亿种元素 编织成天罗地网
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.27,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}就在我脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.98,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}混沌之城 摇摇欲坠
